<div class="site-container">
  <section class="c-content-box">
    <main class="c-content-box__main">
      <div class="c-content-box__main__container">
        <h1>We are starting to meet together again</h1>
        <h2>We would love for you to come and join us; you're welcome to come in person or tune in online.</h2>
        <p>We meet at 4.30pm in Willcox House, 140-148 Borough High Street, SE1 1LB. Please arrive in plenty of time to help with social distancing guidelines. You will need to wear a face covering (<a href="https://fiec.org.uk/resources/wearing-face-masks-at-church" target="_blank" rel="noopener">why?</a>), if possible please <a href="/contact">let us know you are coming</a>, but feel free to just turn up if that is easier for you.</p>
        <a href="https://goo.gl/maps/1ECijwk8QEb1GrKv5" class="u-link u-link--arrowed u-link--black">
          <%= svg_tag('map') %>
          <span>View on a map</span>
        </a>
        
        <a href="/live" class="u-link u-link--arrowed u-link--black">
          <%= svg_tag('video') %>
          <span>Go to the live stream page</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </main>
  </section>
</div>
